decks.notes: The deck focuses on quickly overwhelming the opponent with low-cost creatures like Kor Skyfisher, Squadron Hawk, and Thraben Inspector, backed up by spells like Battle Screech and Guardians' Pledge to pump up the team. Prismatic Strands provides protection while Journey to Nowhere deals with opponent threats. The deck aims to flood the board with creatures and push through damage efficiently, ultimately aiming to swarm the opponent before they can establish a significant defense.
